Description
Google Meet - Auto Mute is your essential Chrome extension for ensuring privacy and control right from the meeting joining page. This powerful tool automatically mutes your microphone and turns off your camera as you prepare to join a Google Meet session, so you never have to worry about accidentally broadcasting audio or video.

Key Features:
Automatic Muting: Mutes your microphone on the meeting joining page, ensuring you enter the meeting quietly.
Camera Control: Turns off your camera on the joining page, giving you peace of mind about your privacy.
Accidental Join Prevention: Prevents unintentional joining with your camera or microphone on, saving you from embarrassing moments.
Seamless Integration: Easily integrates with Google Meet without any complicated setup or configuration.
Whether you're joining a meeting from a noisy environment or just want to ensure your privacy, Google Meet - Auto Mute has got you covered. Install it today and take control of your meeting experience!
